          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The relative Cd-yield data were normalized to mass=111.",
                "The yield of mass=113 was established by smooth extra-",
                "polation of the curve through masses 111 and 112. Then",
                "the yield of mass=114 was obtained by subtraction of",
                "the 113-yield from the normalized measured sum of",
                "relative abundances of masses 113+114.",
                "The tin-yields were matched to the normalized Cd-yields",
                "by placing the 117Sn yield on a smooth curve towards",
                "the normalized 116Cd yield."
              ]
            }
          ],
